# 🚀 Roblox Fly GUI Script

Simple Fly GUI script for Roblox executed using `loadstring`.

## 📜 Script

```lua
loadstring(game:HttpGet("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/10778390-a11y/fly-script/main/fly.lua"))()
```

## ✨ Features

* Button to enable/disable flying
* Smooth camera-based control
* Easy to use
* Lightweight code

## 📦 Installation

1. Copy the `loadstring`
2. Paste it into your executor
3. Run the script

## ⚠️ Note

This script is for educational purposes only.

